<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer17330960880927323342">Tracey-anne lives in London with her family. She loves the diversity of her work as a mixed media artist and writer. <br/><br/>Certified to teach, her world is filled with various forms of creativity. Tracey-anne has exhibited art dolls in a Canadian gallery and has been published in various US magazines.<br/><br/>With her active imagination, mingled with a love of folklore and the old mysteries, she felt inspired to</span>
  <span id="freeText17330960880927323342" style="display:none">Tracey-anne lives in London with her family. She loves the diversity of her work as a mixed media artist and writer. <br /><br />Certified to teach, her world is filled with various forms of creativity. Tracey-anne has exhibited art dolls in a Canadian gallery and has been published in various US magazines.<br /><br />With her active imagination, mingled with a love of folklore and the old mysteries, she felt inspired to write a fictional story revolving around love and karma blending reality with fantasy. Her novel 'A Carpet of Purple Flowers' is the synchronicity of a writer's mind with an artistic heart.<br /><br />Facebook: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.facebook.com/Traceyannemccartney">https://www.facebook.com/Traceyannemc...</a><br />Tumblr: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://acarpetofpurpleflowers.tumblr.com">http://acarpetofpurpleflowers.tumblr.com</a></span>
  <a data-text-id="17330960880927323342" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

